The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should bereported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld statusthe overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should bereported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.2. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld statusthe overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.   (Md. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should bereported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld statusthe overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.   (Md. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should bereported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld statusthe overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should bereported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.2. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, theboard as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time.
